<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.3.2">
<l>tāyniṉainta kaṉṟēyok kaveṉṉai yuntaṉṉai yēniṉaik kaccey tutāṉeṉak</l>
<l>kāyniṉainta ruḷcey yumappaṉai yaṉṟiv vaiyaka muṇṭumiḻn tiṭṭa</l>
<l>vāyaṉai makarakku ḻaikkā taṉaimain taṉaimatiḷ kōvali ṭaikaḻi</l>
<l>yāyaṉai yamarark kariyēṟṟai yeṉaṉ paṉaiyaṉ ṟiyāta riyēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without [my] father who grants me grace, thinking [of me] for my sake,</l>
<l rend="indent">making me think of him, like a calf that thinks of its mother,</l>
<l>The one whose mouth consumed, then expelled, the world, the youth,</l>
<l>The one whose ears have makara earrings, the herder with a herding staff</l>
<l rend="indent">in walled Kōval[ūr],</l>
<l>The male lion of immortals, my beloved, I will not revere [anyone].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
